            <lg xml:id="TK76">
<l>aṟattiṟkē yaṉpucār peṉpa vaṟiyār</l>
<l>maṟattiṟku maḵtē tuṇai</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Know-nothings say that love is an aid to good alone;</l>
<l>it is also a match for hatred.</l>
            </lg>
